                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-283-off1446 t18170917-283-cd1447"></join>, one check, value 11l. 16s. 3d.; another check, value 7l.; another check, value 11l. 10s. 9d.; and one 10l. six 5l. bank notes, and one promissory note for the payment of and value 5l.
            </rs>, the property of 
